summary.summaryText: Recent Bachelor of Marketing & Business Management graduate seeking an internship that will allow for learning the ins and outs of the advertising field and provide an opportunity to add value to ABC Marketing by applying theoretical knowledge into practice. Previous informal experience with social media channel set up and blogging has been gained during university as part of the Campus Newspaper team.
